{"id":134,"parent_id":124,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":134,"title":"Romans 10","subtitle":"","short_title":"Rom.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 10"],[".studySummary",["i","Salvation comes through righteousness to those who believe in Christ—Faith comes by hearing the gospel taught by legal administrators sent of God."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.1","order":"03.08.010.15998"},["b","1"],"Brethren, my heart’s desire and prayer to God for Israel is, that they might be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"saved"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.2","order":"03.08.010.15999"},["b","2"],"For I bear them record that they have a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"zeal"],"of God, but not according to knowledge."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.3","order":"03.08.010.16000"},["b","3"],"For they being ignorant of God’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"righteousness"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"going about"],"to establish their own righteousness, have not",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"submitted"],"themselves unto the righteousness of God."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.4","order":"03.08.010.16001"},["b","4"],"For Christ",["i","is"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"end"],"of the law for righteousness to every one that believeth."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.5","order":"03.08.010.16002"},["b","5"],"For Moses describeth the righteousness which is of the law, That the man which doeth those things shall live by them."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.6","order":"03.08.010.16003"},["b","6"],"But the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"righteousness"],"which is of faith speaketh on this wise, Say not in thine heart, Who shall ascend into heaven? (that is, to bring Christ down",["i","from above:"],")"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.7","order":"03.08.010.16004"},["b","7"],"Or, Who shall descend into the deep? (that is, to bring up Christ again from the dead.)"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.8","order":"03.08.010.16005"},["b","8"],"But what saith it? The word is nigh thee,",["i","even"],"in thy mouth, and in thy heart: that is, the word of faith, which we preach;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.9","order":"03.08.010.16006"},["b","9"],"That if thou shalt confess with thy mouth the Lord Jesus, and shalt believe in thine heart that God hath raised him from the dead, thou shalt be saved."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.10","order":"03.08.010.16007"},["b","10"],"For with the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"heart"],"man",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"believeth"],"unto righteousness; and with the mouth confession is made unto",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"salvation"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.11","order":"03.08.010.16008"},["b","11"],"For the scripture saith, Whosoever believeth on him shall not be ashamed."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.12","order":"03.08.010.16009"},["b","12"],"For there is no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"difference"],"between the Jew and the Greek: for the same Lord over all is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"rich"],"unto all that",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"call"],"upon him."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.13","order":"03.08.010.16010"},["b","13"],"For whosoever shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"call"],"upon the name of the Lord shall be saved."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.14","order":"03.08.010.16011"},["b","14"],"How then shall they call on him in whom they have not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"believed"],"? and how shall they believe in him of whom they have not heard? and how shall they hear without a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"preacher"],"?"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.15","order":"03.08.010.16012"},["b","15"],"And how shall they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"preach"],", except they be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"sent"],"? as it is written, How beautiful are the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"feet"],"of them that preach the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_15d"},"gospel"],"of",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_15e"},"peace"],", and bring glad tidings of good things!"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.16","order":"03.08.010.16013"},["b","16"],"But they have not all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"obeyed"],"the gospel. For Esaias saith, Lord, who hath",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"believed"],"our report?"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.17","order":"03.08.010.16014"},["b","17"],"So then",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"faith"],["i","cometh"],"by",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"hearing"],", and hearing by the word of God."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.18","order":"03.08.010.16015"},["b","18"],"But I say, Have they not heard? Yes verily, their sound went into all the earth, and their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"words"],"unto the ends of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"world"],"."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.19","order":"03.08.010.16016"},["b","19"],"But I say, Did not Israel know? First Moses saith, I will provoke you to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"jealousy"],"by",["i","them that are"],"no people,",["i","and"],"by a foolish nation I will anger you."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.20","order":"03.08.010.16017"},["b","20"],"But",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"Esaias"],"is very bold, and saith, I was found of them that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"sought"],"me not; I was made manifest unto them that asked not after me."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.21","order":"03.08.010.16018"},["b","21"],"But to Israel he saith, All day long I have stretched forth my hands unto a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"disobedient"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"gainsaying"],"people."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.1a","order":"03.08.010.16019"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reconciliation"},"TG Reconciliation"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.2a","order":"03.08.010.16021"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zeal"},"TG Zeal"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.3a","order":"03.08.010.16023"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-the-standard-of-righteousness"},"TG God, the Standard of Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.3b","order":"03.08.010.16025"},["b","3b"],["span.small","GR"],"desiring, endeavoring."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.3c","order":"03.08.010.16027"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/submissiveness"},"Submissiveness"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.4a","order":"03.08.010.16029"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.7.7-10"},"2 Ne. 2:7 (7–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.6a","order":"03.08.010.16031"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.10a","order":"03.08.010.16033"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heart"},"TG Heart"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.10b","order":"03.08.010.16035"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.14.11-14"},"D&C 46:14 (11–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.10c","order":"03.08.010.16037"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation"},"TG Salvation"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.12a","order":"03.08.010.16039"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/10.35.34-35"},"Acts 10:35 (34–35)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/2.11"},"Rom. 2:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.28.26-29"},"Gal. 3:28 (26–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.12b","order":"03.08.010.16041"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.12c","order":"03.08.010.16043"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-access-to"},"TG God, Access to"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.13a","order":"03.08.010.16045"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prayer"},"TG Prayer"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.14a","order":"03.08.010.16047"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hypocrisy"},"Hypocrisy"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.14b","order":"03.08.010.16049"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.6"},"D&C 42:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.15a","order":"03.08.010.16051"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/missionary-work"},"TG Missionary Work"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/preaching"},"Preaching"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.15b","order":"03.08.010.16053"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/called-of-god"},"TG Called of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.15c","order":"03.08.010.16055"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.15"},"Nahum 1:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"15d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.15d","order":"03.08.010.16057"},["b","15d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gospel"},"TG Gospel"],"."],["div",{"id":"15e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.15e","order":"03.08.0